              Llamar Ahora
            </a>
            <a 
              href="mailto:jbueno@sdgestion.es"
              class="w-full inline-flex items-center justify-center px-6 py-3 border-2 border-white text-white rounded-md font-medium hover:bg-white hover:text-primary-600 transition-colors"
